 financiaci\u00f3n y reestructuraci\u00f3n, la sindicaci\u00f3n y la financiaci\u00f3n puente, concretamente inmobiliaria, en Suiza.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-e52a442\" data-id=\"e52a442\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d7c14a0 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"d7c14a0\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<style>\/*! elementor - v3.15.0 - 20-08-2023 *\/\n.elementor-widget-image{text-align:center}.elementor-widget-image a{display:inline-block}.elementor-widget-image a img[src$=\".svg\"]{width:48px}.elementor-widget-image img{vertical-align:middle;display:inline-block}<\/style>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"999\" height=\"562\" src=\"https:\/\/www.banquecramer.ch\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Bauer.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-image-11207\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.banquecramer.ch\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Bauer.jpg 999w, https:\/\/www.banquecramer.ch\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Bauer-300x169.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.banquecramer.ch\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/Bauer-768x432.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 999px) 100vw, 999px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-32e607d elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"32e607d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Dr. Michael E. Bauer, CPA,